Class Service

java.lang.Object
Service
public class Service extends Object
Contains the data from any given service provided to a member by a provider Service constructor is called in provider, and Service data is stored in ServiceList Functions only as a buffer between the .txt file data is stored in and the users accessing ServiceList
Version:
1.0
Author:
Liam Tucker

      public String validService(String servDate, String provNum, String membNum, String servCode, String comments)
      Checks if all of the data is the proper length.
      Parameters:
      servDate - is in format MM-DD-YYYY
      provNum - is in format 12345678
      membNum - is in format 123456789
      servCode - is in format 123456
      comments - is at most 100 characters long
      Returns:
      errorMessage
